{"tid":1441223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺得立場有問題嘅入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-10T15:18:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T15:50:33.000Z","uid":252353,"like":80,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4c9eb06c5121395bddcb33597c27c975db9e2686","tid":1441223,"uid":252353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:18:52.000Z","msg":"記者嘅職責就係報導事實嘅全部<br />\n有人出去示威亦都係事實<br />\n立場記者報導又有咩問題<br />\n<br />\n我哋當初支持立場唔係因為立場幫我哋<br />\n而係因為佢係中立 報導事實嘅全部<br />\n而唔似TVB 只報導對政權有利嘅新聞<br />\n如果立場只報黑警濫權 ，同TVB有乜分別？<br />\n<br />\n同埋抗爭咗都兩個幾月 口罩+頭巾包耳仔個個都要知<br />\n發夢時自己有責任保護自己 <br />\n記者影乜都係佢哋自由"},{"pid":"03d1dcfeee6f59dea527d593d2559925afc0bbea","tid":1441223,"uid":131842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"@2318 <a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=y7g0wjbeyFmnVC7InFCgMvcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=506256fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n71Px9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn71Px9b.png&h=179f3e74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長期置頂] [iOS/Android/PC/Mac] 香城online正式加入地圖功能<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438115\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438115</a>"},{"pid":"e1e3dfea4882ad27b30d716f0ddbeeccc9197232","tid":1441223,"uid":252353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f92580395f4cdbfb4d00714b84e31239b1f5bf47","tid":1441223,"uid":252353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"仲有 三毛死全家"},{"pid":"383894921ba4b4cc21919d0e8e5a6596822ff0d4","tid":1441223,"uid":252353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ab8c20a4d8ebe4da6bfcb11a38e6f50d4584108","tid":1441223,"uid":252353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T15:21:01